  "notes": "Route 31 is a short east-west route bridging Route 30 (west) and Violet City (east) via the Violet Gate. The route is notable for the Kenya mail delivery sidequest (Elm's errand payoff), TM50 Nightmare reward, and the western entrance to Dark Cave. Bug Catcher Wade is the sole trainer with Pokegear rematch support across five fight tiers. Pokecrystal source: maps/Route31.asm. Dimensions: 20x9 blocks (40x18 tiles)."
